                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_842">p. 842</ref>, records
                    that Roosevelt dined with the Churchill family and Hopkins, and that Roosevelt
                    and Churchill were closeted for several hours following dinner. No record of the
                    discussion during or after dinner has been found.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
